    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Dominicus">Dominichi</name></persName>
                        riceve da <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>
                        gratia Dei sancte Lucane ecclesie humulis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>,
                        per cartula livellario nomine, casa et res illa in loco et finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/2102">Cassio</placeName>, pertinentes ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatus</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, quas ego antea ad manus mea abuit; casa vero ipsa cum
                        fundamento et edeficio suo, seo curte, orto, terris, vineis, olivis, silvis,
                        virgareis, pratis, pascuis, cultas res vel incultas, omnia quantum ego ipsi
                        antea exinde ad manus mea abuit (…). Obbligo: ego vel meis heredes in ipsa
                        casa residere et abitare debeamus et tam ipsa casa et res quas mihi dedisti
                        bene laborare et gubernare seo meliorare debeamus (…). Censo: tibi vel ad
                        successoribus tuis ad pars ipsius episcopatui Sancti Martini per singulos
                        annos, in ipso loco Cassio, reddere debeamus de vino sistaria decem et octo,
                        ad tale sistario quale in ipso loco percurrit; et per omnem mense decembrio
                        vobis reddere debeamus in suprascripto loco per nos aut per misso nostro,
                        vobis vel ad misso vestro, argentum denarios bonos expendiviles numero
                        decem; et de quinto in quinto anno vobis reddere debeamus uno montone bono
                        et uno saccho; et a mandato vestro venire debeamus hic Luca legem et
                        iustitiam faciendum tantum (…). Pena: ego qui supra Andreas una cum meis
                        heredes conponere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos viginti (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        notarius scrive due <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>.
                        Actum <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>:
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Danihel">Daniel</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Allo">Aloni</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Angelbertus"
                        >Anghalperti</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Marinus"
                                >Marinus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Flaipertus">Flaipertus</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Lopo">Lopi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Alpertus">Alpertus</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
